<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> yāyamu cīramalavaṁ bādika bhaṁḍikaṭṭaṁ bādika talakaṭṭaṁ vīsāmu sāliyacīrabhaṁḍikaṭṭa naḍḍuvudalakaṭṭaṁ bādika Īsaṁtta nammina soliyacīra gaddenāna vīsāmu pōṁka peṟka nūṟu vōṁka
<lb n="3" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> munaṁ dellaṁ beṟka naḍḍaṁḍu Ullivasapu soṁṭhi bellamu modalugā ne<unclear>ttiṭi kha</unclear>ṁḍamunaṁ dellaṁ beṟkanemulamu gaṁccugaddenānaṁ gā<unclear>ni</unclear>yuṁgā nicitimi nela <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> pōṁkapeṟka māṟu vōṁkalu te
